node.text:
#dubaifurniture #dubailuxury We present you an incredibly elegant interior design — our new successful project of a spacious apartment worthy of Expo 2020 Dubai, located in one of the elite residential complexes. The iconic island destination, Blue Waters Dubai — is the best place to live!  This fantastic apartment is the brainchild of Luxury Antonovich Design Company. The author of all ideas is the chief designer and architect — Katrina Antonovich.
Just from the front door you can understand how stylish and fashionable this luxurious apartment is. Meanwhile, the main design motive in the project is a majestic modern style, designed to soften and combine a variety of inspirational objects into a single composition. The emphasis is on elegance, which is shaded by exquisite lines. In everything from crystal chandeliers to stone finishes, style and sophistication can be traced. Glossy surfaces and large mirrors double the shine, emphasizing the luxury of the rooms.  #furnituremaker #furnitureonline #interiors #architecture #interiorforinspo #interiordesire #details #uniqueinteriors #myinteriors #refinedinteriors #luxurydevelopment #refined #luxuryinteriordesign #luxurydesign

node.text:
Luxury Antonovich Home — the best company of furniture production and sale — is a modern enterprise in Dubai that has its own manufacture of the most modern designer furniture models in a wide assortment. The working credo of our company is a constant desire for improvement and development.
The best designer furniture and interior items — carpets, curtains, lighting fixtures and interior design ideas, presented in our showroom organically combine such traditional qualities as style, comfort, convenience, ergonomics, environmental cleanliness of the materials used with modern design and beauty

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich on July 25, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'CHANEL CHANEL'.

node.text:
Every day we have plenty of opportunities to make our life better, brighter, happier🦋💖
Focus on positive emotions and actions, they will bring you to the future you are dreaming of!🤗😉

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich in Rolls Royce. May be an image of one or more people, people standing, outdoors and text that says 'R ROLLS-ROYCE MOTOR CARS ISTANBUL T'.

node.text: I think nowadays it is very important to be that strong woman and to follow your passions regardless of what your situation is. We should keep ourself together and balance our life perfectly.💛👌👍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich in CHANEL. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and text that says 'CHANEL CH CHANEL CHA CHANE'.

node.text:
There is no amount of success, money or other material benefits that can take the place of time spent with your family! These are precious and magical moments... The only time I feel myself as safe as possible..is around my family!💞💞🤗🤗
Let's cherish any chance we have to spend some time with our loved ones! 💖

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich in Dior. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: The greatest gift that you can give yourself is a little bit of your own attention and self-love. It's a huge blessing to spend some time just for yourself! Enjoy it as much as you can, guys! 🙌👌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people sitting and outdoors.

node.text: Choosing to be positive and having a grateful attitude is going to determine how you're going to live your life. I try to surround myself with good people who make me feel great and give me positive energy.💕💕💕

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich on July 21, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and body of water.

node.text: The time we spend with loved ones is priceless💞💕

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich in Bodrum, Mugla. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
Happy Birthday To Me 🎂🎊🎈🎁💐
Thanks for all birthday wishes, my lovely people!💖
You make a great day even greater!🤗🙌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sitting and outdoors.

node.text:
What is your biggest dream, my dear?🥰
I hope my stories inspire everyone out there to keep chasing their dreams. You can go slow. Allow your dreams and goals to change, but live an intentional life.😉👌🙌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich on July 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and body of water.

node.text:
I feel like I’m floating in the middle of a dream...🥰
A dream I don’t ever want to wake up from.⭐️⭐️⭐️
I feel so grateful for the life I get to live. I’m so thankful for the people I have in my life and all the love that surrounds me. Hope you feel the same, my dears! 💋❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sunglasses and outdoors.

node.text: I hope this weekend was good to you, and helped you to recharge, gain strength and spend incredible time with your friends and family!🙌💦

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich in Dior. May be an image of 1 person, standing, scooter and outdoors.

node.text: My advice is to enjoy the journey of your life, my friends, and try to make it better every day. And never lose the passion and the love for what you do! 👌🙌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Katrina Antonovich on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and body of water.

node.text:
Very little is needed to make a happy life!💫✨
It is all within yourself, in your way of thinking! In order to be truly happy, you must embrace the imperfection that is part of life. By trying to make things perfect you will waste your lifetime!❤️💋
